title: 303 Nysaye Oneno Ka Winyo Odwaro Gore Piny

lines: 1. Nyasaye oneno ka winyoodwaro gore piny;Ka En ohero winyo cha,ang`eyo kohera.
Oheroa, oheroa,ang`eyo kohera;Ka En ohero winyo cha,ang`eyo kohera.
2. Thiepe duto manie e piny,Nyasaye nochweyogi;Ka Nyasaye ohero thiepe,ang`eyo kohera.
3. Nyasaye olosogi duto,kendo oritogi;To an bende oparo an,ang`eyo kohera.
